{"word":"G4277 - προέπω - proépō - pro-ep'-o - Forewarn","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προέπω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">proépō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pro-ep'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Forewarn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - முன்னறிவி, முன்னே சொல்"},{"paragraph":"to say beforehand; to warn in advance to predict"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4253 - πρό - pró - pro/4253\">G4253</a> and <a href=\"#/G2036 - ἔπω - épō - ep'-o/2036\">G2036</a>; to <i>say already</i>, to <i>predict</i>: - forewarn, say (speak, tell) before. Compare <a href=\"#/G4280 - προερέω - proeréō - pro-er-eh'-o/4280\">G4280</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}